35
00:03:17,570 --> 00:03:21,610
I wouldn't be working in a dump like this if it wasn't for that.

36
00:03:21,610 --> 00:03:23,290
Hey, you...

37
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,750
Excuse me.

38
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,270
It's a woman,

39
00:03:35,270 --> 00:03:36,900
and a beauty at that.

40
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:38,680
