41
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:41,080
Investigator's intuition.

42
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:44,280
How many times have you gotten in trouble because of that intuition?

43
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,930
Don't be deceived, boss.

44
00:03:47,330 --> 00:03:49,120
I don't care if I'm deceived.

45
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,980
No, more than that...

46
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:54,140
I want to be deceived.

47
00:03:55,290 --> 00:03:59,150
So this is a genuine request?

48
00:03:59,150 --> 00:04:01,630
Um, what else would it be?

49
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:04,640
Well, debt collectors, for example...

50
00:04:04,640 --> 00:04:05,560
Nothing!

51
00:04:06,610 --> 00:04:09,910
A search for a missing cat, though?

52
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:16,130
Yes. My husband Yuzuki and I loved her as if she was our own child.

53
00:04:16,910 --> 00:04:21,530
If Mii-chan were gone, it would cause Yuzuki grief.

54
00:04:22,090 --> 00:04:24,320
So you haven't told your husband yet?

55
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:26,740
Oh, I'm sorry.

56
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:29,180
My husband passed away quite some time ago.

57
00:04:29,610 --> 00:04:31,540
Oh, I'm sorry about your loss.

58
00:04:32,770 --> 00:04:35,810
