63
00:04:44,790 --> 00:04:47,150
No, it's not that.

64
00:04:47,150 --> 00:04:51,820
Maybe a dog, but a cat is somewhat out of my hands.

65
00:04:51,820 --> 00:04:54,100
How about five hundred thousand yen?

66
